<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4411417>
    dc:description "FIGURES 12–13. Wing venation of Vareuptychia themis comb. nov.: 12. male; 13. female. Black arrows indicate generic diagnostic features. Scale bar = 2 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4411417/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4411419>
    dc:description "FIGURES 14–23. Male genitalia of species of Vareuptychia stat. rest.: 14–18. Vareuptychia similis comb. rest. (BMNH#1420973): 14. lateral, 15. dorsal; 16. ventral; 17. aedeagus, dorsal; 18. aedeagus, lateral; 19–23. Vareuptychia themis comb. nov. (BMNH#1420750): 19. lateral; 20. dorsal; 21. ventral; 22. aedeagus, dorsal; 23. aedeagus, lateral. Scale bar = 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4411419/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4411421>
    dc:description "FIGURES 24–27. Female genitalia of species of Vareuptychia stat. rest.: 24–25. Vareuptychia similis comb. rest. (DZUP 27.891): 24. lateral, 25. ventral; 26–27. Vareuptychia themis comb. nov. (DZUP 27.897): 26. lateral; 27. ventral. Scale bar = 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4411421/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4411456>
    dc:description "FIGURE 87. Phylogenetic tree showing the position of Vareuptychia stat. rest. (green) and Vanima gen. nov. (purple) in Euptychiina. Numbers above the branches indicate the support values (SH-aLRT support/ultrafast bootstrap support); numbers below 70 are not shown." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4411456/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

